===[[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]===
{{main|Dawn (Space-Time Smackdown 154)}}
Dawn makes an appearance as a {{TCG|Supporter}} card in [[Pokémon Trading Card Game Pocket]]'s second expansion, {{TCGP|Space-Time Smackdown}}. When the player plays this card, they can move an {{TCG|Energy}} from one of their Benched Pokémon to their Active Pokémon. 

